title: Windows Neptune Unreleased OS Build 5111
description:
Windows Neptune was
      +----------------------Brought to you by Alphon--------------------------+
Windows Neptune was the experimental home-version of Windows NT, and the predecessor to the widely pirated and used Windows XP.
The special thing about Windows neptune was its difficulty to obtain. A few years back, there was a download on the popular website osvirtual.net(downloads no longer work). A few other mirrors are located on the deep web(tor network) and can be found on indexes and wikis there.

[File info]
Format:VMware Virtual machine
Size:600 Mb
Requrements:Vmware Player or workstation, 0.5+ GHz of cpu power and 500Mb+ RAM
